Title: Dawn of the Infinite: Chrono-Lord Deios
Description:
Chrono-Lord Deios must be behind this all. As the leader of the infinites, he's sure to have led this invasion. I bet Morchie is working for him too.

Let's head into the Bronze Temple! We need to stop Deios before he ruins the true timeline.
PortraitGiverText: Though Deios now commands the infinites, his ambition is to ensure the rise of Murozond, their true leader.
